code for Grails intro. demo made on Oct. 2011
Grails 2.0.0.M2
90 Min. introduction to Grails framwork while building file sharing service with: 
* Grails concept & project structure 
* basic configuration 
* GORM
* Web with controllers and GSP
* file upload
* Plug-ins - Spring seurity for authentication
* Java Melody for monitoring
